HEADWORD: Zander
<hw>Zan"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. D.
<ets>zand</ets> sand.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A European pike
perch (<spn>Stizostedion lucioperca</spn>) allied to the wall-eye; --
called also <altname>sandari</altname>, <altname>sander</altname>,
<altname>sannat</altname>, <altname>schill</altname>, and
<altname>zant</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

